{"words":[{"word":"weeks","count":2},{"word":"looks","count":2},{"word":"causing","count":1},{"word":"trouble","count":1},{"word":"masked","count":1},{"word":"brothers'","count":1},{"word":"turf","count":1},{"word":"afraid","count":1},{"word":"ones","count":1},{"word":"rebuilding","count":1},{"word":"black","count":1},{"word":"alley","count":1},{"word":"hand","count":1},{"word":"coin","count":1},{"word":"eh","count":1},{"word":"wait","count":1},{"word":"mercy","count":1},{"word":"blind","count":1},{"word":"please","count":1},{"word":"time","count":1},{"word":"yeah","count":1},{"word":"ago","count":1},{"word":"hell","count":1},{"word":"racket","count":1},{"word":"thought","count":1},{"word":"whole","count":1},{"word":"place","count":1},{"word":"falling","count":1},{"word":"apart","count":1},{"word":"turns","count":1},{"word":"bloody","count":1},{"word":"terror","count":1},{"word":"woman","count":1},{"word":"saw","count":1},{"word":"word","count":1},{"word":"pulled","count":1},{"word":"blade","count":1},{"word":"lucky","count":1},{"word":"away","count":1},{"word":"took","count":1},{"word":"two","count":1},{"word":"everything's","count":1},{"word":"good","count":1},{"word":"quietly","count":1},{"word":"something","count":1},{"word":"folks","count":1},{"word":"fear","count":1},{"word":"soft","count":1},{"word":"halfway","count":1},{"word":"worked","count":1},{"word":"death","count":1},{"word":"liked","count":1},{"word":"chances","count":1}],"lines":[{"text":"Who's causing trouble here?! Don't you know this is the Masked Brothers' turf?","quest_name":"A Blaze in the Dark","quest_id":158800014},{"text":"What's there to be afraid of? We are the ones rebuilding the Black Alley!","quest_name":"A Blaze in the Dark","quest_id":158800014},{"text":"Now, how about you hand over some coin, eh?","quest_name":"A Blaze in the Dark","quest_id":158800014},{"text":"Wait, mercy! We were blind. Please just let us go this time!","quest_name":"A Blaze in the Dark","quest_id":158800014},{"text":"Yeah, weeks ago. There was one hell of a racket. We thought the whole place was falling apart.","quest_name":"A Blaze in the Dark","quest_id":158800014},{"text":"Turns out, it was a bloody terror of a woman. Saw us, didn't say a word, just pulled a blade on us.","quest_name":"A Blaze in the Dark","quest_id":158800014},{"text":"We were lucky to get away. Took us two weeks to come back.","quest_name":"A Blaze in the Dark","quest_id":158800014},{"text":"Then... everything's good now, right? We'll just be on our way.","quest_name":"A Blaze in the Dark","quest_id":158800014},{"text":"Quietly...","quest_name":"A Blaze in the Dark","quest_id":158800014},{"text":"Well you got to have something to make folks fear you, right? One of you looks soft, and the other looks halfway worked to death... I liked my chances.","quest_name":"A Blaze in the Dark","quest_id":158800014},{"text":"Not even once!!!","quest_name":"A Blaze in the Dark","quest_id":158800014}]}